o cluster samples. This points to X-ray\nunderluminous clusters being younger systems than normal clusters, possibly in\nthe process of accreting groups of galaxies, individual galaxies and gas.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Mar 2014 18:07:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
