ll provide a deeper investigation of\nthe secular evolution ($\\sim 100\\,$Myr) of the KB over its whole mass spectrum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Mar 2014 11:36:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Apr 2014 10:21:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 27 Aug 2014 15:37:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
